<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1367852" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/eddy-cue-british-telecom.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="420" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/eddy-cue-british-telecom.jpg 800w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/eddy-cue-british-telecom-360x189.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/eddy-cue-british-telecom-768x403.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></p>
