<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1367856" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/MSFT-Nadella-OpenAI-Altman-09-official-joint-pic-1.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="637" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/MSFT-Nadella-OpenAI-Altman-09-official-joint-pic-1.jpg 1000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/MSFT-Nadella-OpenAI-Altman-09-official-joint-pic-1-360x229.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/MSFT-Nadella-OpenAI-Altman-09-official-joint-pic-1-768x489.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
