<p>▲ Bose 汽车音响</p>
</div>
<p>爱范君也在现场领先体验了 Bose 消噪耳塞。</p>
<p>耳塞设计简洁优雅、身形精巧，新耳塞佩戴起来比前几代更舒适稳定；降噪等级切换便捷自然，消噪效果明显，最高消噪级别下能够消除周边大部分噪音；听感上低频表现很好，鼓点饱满而富有冲击力。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1368022" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/0dsmzXFDoJDHVTDF.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/0dsmzXFDoJDHVTDF.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/0dsmzXFDoJDHVTDF-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/0dsmzXFDoJDHVTDF-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/0dsmzXFDoJDHVTDF-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
